    "causal_summary": "Every skill's feature_catalog/NN--<name>/ and manual_testing_playbook/NN--<name>/ category folders carry a two-digit NN-- ordinal prefix. No runtime consumer parses that number — ordering already lives in the root index tables — yet the prefix is load-bearing in exactly one place (the sk-doc validator classifies a catalog/playbook leaf only when its parent matches ^\\\\d{2}--).",
